            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Sophie. Why do you seem to be in such a hurry?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Have you seen Oskar around anywhere? I'm searching for him..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oskar? That reminds me, I saw him run off towards the lake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes. His appearance is very... Unique. I doubt I would mistake him for another person."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Ahaha, you're right. Although he wasn't so rotund in the past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I don't know why, but he suddenly gets really fat, and suddenly gets really skinny."
